See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CodeJamSession
    CodeJamSession is the main API entry point, which consists in logging to a code jam platform hostname and then providing facilities such as :
    Retrieves contest, round Interacts with platform API from a given round Downloads input Submits solutions
    Contest
    POJO class that represents a Google Jam Contest.
    Round
    POJO class that represents a Google Jam Round.

Package fr.faylixe.googlecodejam.client Description

Google Code Jam client API consists in several components, namely :

  • An API entry point for managing a contest session through command such as download, submit, etc ...
  • A command line application.
  • Common model object for interacting with Google Code Jam webservices.
